reviewText: The only downfall is that the audio is not in 5.1, is stereo, but sound is excellent and the song collection is very good.

I will consider discovering Karen Souza as a singer to be my plus for 2015 along with Phyllis Chapell.
Hope she will deliver a new album for 2016. Great selection and umpicable performance vocal and instrumental.
After hearing Karen on a number of cover compilations I found her three albums Essentials 1 and 2 and Hotel souza ..I just needed to add the DVD to our collection
